    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Underworld. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.IcpF4hZrSJAJdnJf]{Safehouse Network}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Society checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.AJstokjdG6iDjVjE]{Impersonate}. At 17th level, if you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Zf4yiLDdxHPovEQI]{Legendary Codebreaker}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.n0S0tJiOJPQk0Rne]{Legendary Linguist}, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
